WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Pwaps' is a Workbench game played on a diamond shaped board,
where you swap tiles located on either sides and over and under
a clicked tile. The idea is to place as many tiles of the same
type together as possible. When tiles of the same type are next
to each other, they are then removed and replaced by new tiles.

  The more tiles of the same type that are put together, the more
points you get.

  Have fun!

